snippet.title: Best VGM 1182 - Shantae : Risky's Revenge - Through the Trees
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS / iOS
Shantae : Risky's Revenge (2010)
Through the Trees
Jake Kaufman
